  contentShort: Doesn't have children
  content: "Due to unforeseen circumstances, the head of TUDAWR, previously known
    as TOAEIPE was forced to resign.\n\nBut this is an opportunity for a new beginning!
    \n\nWe are happy to introduce: The Independent Institute For Labour Freedom.
    Or short TIIFLF! "
